com.gmail.socraticphoenix.asmsig.type

Interface TypeSignaturePart

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    TypeInformal
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TypeArray, TypeFill, TypeInner, TypeParameterized, TypeVar, TypeVarRef, TypeWild

    public interface TypeSignaturePart
    Represents an element of a signature or an element of an element of a signature. All TypeSignatureParts are mutable so that they can be built up through ASM's visitor pattern, but you are strongly advised not to mutate them yourself after they have first been initialized.
